WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.735
When they're done, the trainee clicks “Submit my work”.

00:00:03.735 --> 00:00:05.840
The platform gathers everything

00:00:05.840 --> 00:00:08.080
companies, proposals and consents

00:00:08.080 --> 00:00:12.019
and sends it to the trainer, with the trainee's signature.

00:00:12.019 --> 00:00:13.920
They can submit up to twice.
